Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:30.04,TEXT4,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(234,262)}海猴
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.03,0:11:30.04,TEXT3,,0,0,0,,{\c&H3598ED&\fs50\pos(646,622)\frz5}菊石
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:30.04,TEXT4,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(646,622)\frz5}菊石
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.03,0:11:30.04,TEXT3,,0,0,0,,{\c&H9327E0&\fs50\frz5\frz-10\pos(1460,646)}改造人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:30.04,TEXT4,,0,0,0,,{\c&H9327E0&\fs50\frz5\frz-10\pos(1460,646)}改造人
